	      </tr>
            </table>

   <p>For earlier references to this money and George Mercers accounts, see <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-04-02-0147&amp;expandNote=GEWN-02-04-02-0147-fn-0002#GEWN-02-04-02-0147-fn-0002" class="document">John Kirkpatrick to GW, 19 June 1757, particularly note 2</a>, and <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-04-02-0190&amp;expandNote=GEWN-02-04-02-0190-fn-0004#GEWN-02-04-02-0190-fn-0004" class="document">GW to Robinson, 10 July 1757, particularly note 4.</a></p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-04-02-0206-fn-0004-ptr" id="GEWN-02-04-02-0206-fn-0004">4</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-04-02-0190&amp;expandNote=GEWN-02-04-02-0190-fn-0005#GEWN-02-04-02-0190-fn-0005" class="document">GW to Robinson, 10 July 1757, n.5.</a> This may be 3s. 4d.</p>

